Company Description                    




                        Metkore Alloys & Industries Ltd.(MAIL) engages in the manufacture and trade of high carbon ferro-chrome for use in the stainless steel industry in India. The company manufactures metal alloys in various grades, including silicon manganese and ferro silicon. MAIL also exports its products. The company, formerly known as Cronimet Alloys India Limited, was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Hyderabad.                    


